text: Bennett Run is a U.S. Geological Survey. National Hydrography Dataset high- resolution flowline data. The National Map, accessed March 24, 2019 tributary of Conewago Creek in York County, Pennsylvania in the United States. The Kise Mill Bridge spans Bennett Run in Newberry Township. ==See also== *List of rivers of Pennsylvania ==References== Category:Rivers of Pennsylvania Category:Tributaries of the Susquehanna River Category:Rivers of York County, Pennsylvania
